
MOUSE:
Mouse button 1 - selecting
Mouse button 2 - default action for selection
Mouse button 3 - first person view
Wheel - zoom in/out


CAMERA:
Up/Down/Left/Right - scroll view

Home/Num8 - kig op
End/Num2 - kig ned
Insert/Num6 - rotate left
Delete/Num4 - roteta right
Pressing f - first person view

PageDown/Num3 - zoom in
PageUp/Num9 - zoom out
Pressing z - zooming in and out by moving mouse up and down

Space/Num5 - mapmode
Tab - jump to latest notifier

Esc - go to game menu


GROUPING:
Ctrl+1-9 - create a group of the selected units
1-9 - select group
double press 1-9 - jump to group


UNIT:
m - move
a - attack
g - gather or repair
q - build quater
r - build armory
t - build tower
s - chieftain magic1
c - chieftain magic2


QUARTERS:
[Ctrl|Shift] p - exit peons
c - train chieftain
r - place rally point


ARMORY:
g - gather resources menu
w - produce weapons menu
a - deploy army menu
t - transport resources menu
r - place rally point

	RESOURCES MENU:
	[Ctrl|Shift] t - assign peons to gather tree
	[Ctrl|Shift] r - assign peons to gather rock
	[Ctrl|Shift] i - assign peons to gather iron
	[Ctrl|Shift] c - assign peons to gather tropical chickens
	Esc - back to armory menu

	WEAPONS MENU:
	[Ctrl|Shift] r - order rock weapons
	[Ctrl|Shift] i - order iron weapons
	[Ctrl|Shift] c - order chicken weapons
	Esc - back to armory menu

	ARMY MENU:
	[Ctrl|Shift] p - exit peons
	[Ctrl|Shift] r - exit rock warriors
	[Ctrl|Shift] i - exit iron warriors
	[Ctrl|Shift] c - exit chicken warriors
	Esc - back to armory menu
	
	TRANSPORT MENU:
	[Ctrl|Shift] t - exit peons with tree
	[Ctrl|Shift] r - exit peons with rock
	[Ctrl|Shift] i - exit peons with iron
	[Ctrl|Shift] c - exit peons with chicken
	Esc - back to armory menu
	

TOWER:
a - attack
x - exit tower


MULTIPLAYER:
Enter - opens chat window
Shift+Enter - opens chat window with "Send to team" as default
Ctrl+b - create a beacon


CHAT COMMANDS:
/msg nick message - send message to nick
/info nick - show info about nick
/ignore nick - ignores nick
/unignore nick - unignores nick
/ignorelist - show list of nicks ignored


OPTIONS:
+ - increase game speed
- - decrease game speed
Ctrl+a - toggle aggressive units
Ctrl+h - toggle native cursor
Ctrl+s - take a screenshot
